# Upgrade Kundali Matching & Varshphal to Professional Astrologer-Grade Reports + Fix PDF

## Problem

An astrologer reviewed the paid features and confirmed they are far too basic for a paid product:

### Kundali Matching (Current State — ~1 page)
- Only shows: Total score circle + 8 Koota one-line scores
- **Missing**: Boy/Girl individual charts, planetary tables, Manglik analysis per person, Bhakoot/Nadi dosha explanations, detailed interpretive text for each Koota, recommendation section, remedies

### Annual Varshphal (Current State — ~1 page)  
- Only shows: 3 stat cards (Muntha, Muntha Lord, Year Lord) + 2 charts + 1 paragraph
- **Missing**: Full planetary position tables for both charts, Pancha-Adhikari lord system, Tajika Yoga analysis, house-by-house prediction, Dasha for the year, remedies section, month-by-month forecast

### PDF/Print (Broken)
- `@media print` CSS only targets `#kundaliResult` — the Matching and Varshphal result sections are actively hidden by the rule `.card:not(#kundaliResult .card)` which hides ALL cards that aren't inside `#kundaliResult`

